tool_description: An api which contains detailed information about Elden ring along with images.
name: Elden Ring Wiki
title: Elden Ring Wiki

api_list.name: Locations
api_list.description: Locations in elden ring (Maps will be included later)
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://elden-ring-wiki.p.rapidapi.com/locations"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "elden-ring-wiki.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
